                  </hi>. I am a gingerbread<lb></lb>baker. I had a booth in Batter-sea-fair—I had a great-coat at the front of the booth, between the canis-ters and a chair—I am confident it was safe about half-past five o'clock, and I missed it afterwards—I did not see the prisoner there—this is my coat.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
